        <source>"Type a partial container ID in the search box and click the search button to find a Container." &amp; CrLf &amp; CrLf &amp;
"To add a new Damage Report, click the 'Edit' button, and enter the correct values using the combo boxes in the table. When done, click 'Save'. If you wish to remove a Damage Report, select the empty value in the combo boxes for each column and it will be removed.

Clicking 'Cancel' will remove any changes made before the 'Save' button is clicked."</source>
